===Noun===
'''гласность''' (glasnost')

# Publicity, Openness
# Soviet policy of the 1980s. Mikhail Gorbachev began to promote a policy of openness in public discussions about current and historical problems. The policy was termed glasnost [publicity or openness]. This would then be coupled with [[perestroika]].

